{"title":"The New Mavic Comete SL Mips Helmet Promises Perfect Blend of Airflow and Speed","link":"https://bikerumor.com/mavic-comete-sl-mips-helmet/","date":1734361859000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-hero-jpeg.webp\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" alt=\"(Photos / Mavic)\" /></p>\n<p>Mavic just launched a new helmet that promises an ideal mix of protection, aerodynamics, and comfort. Introducing the <a href=\"https://www.mavic.com/en-us/p/comete-sl-mips-hr2401?variant=10576\" target=\"_blank\">Comete SL Mips Helmet</a> that is built to perform on the road, gravel, and XC trails.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-glasses-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-glasses-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Mavic Comete SL Mips Helmet glasses\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-glasses-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-glasses-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-glasses-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-glasses-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-glasses-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-glasses-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos / Mavic)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Mavic says their commitment and focus for the Comete SL is safety and performance while keeping you cool, comfortable and streamlined. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-wind-tunnels-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-wind-tunnels-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Mavic Comete SL Mips Helmet wind tunnels\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-wind-tunnels-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-wind-tunnels-297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-wind-tunnels-120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-wind-tunnels-768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-wind-tunnels-1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Comete SL’s front vents connect to inner ventilation channels to help create airflow to cool the inside of the helmet. It also uses an aero-optimized shape that has been tested in Geneva Wind Tunnels. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-inside-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1044\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-inside-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Mavic Comete SL Mips Helmet inside\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-inside-jpeg.webp 1044w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-inside-245x300.webp 245w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-inside-98x120.webp 98w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-inside-768x942.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Ergo Hold SL+ is a retention system that offers “pinpoint adjustability and comfortable head hold”. Autofit straps go around your ears, don’t twist, and are said to fit seamlessly with all glasses. We’ve seen Autofit on other helmets, and it’s a cool system – the ear cradle is essentially fixed, but it rides on tubular straps and ‘automatically’ positions itself on the tubular strap in the best position for the rider. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-turning-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-turning-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Mavic Comete SL Mips Helmet turning\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-turning-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-turning-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-turning-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-turning-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-turning-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-turning-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Using XRD memory foam on the forehead helps to increase comfort. Need to safely store your prized sunglasses? Mavic has it covered, as the Comete SL’s Glass Garage allows you to store your shades when you need to take them off. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-blue-side-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"1223\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-blue-side-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Mavic Comete SL Mips Helmet blue side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-blue-side-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-blue-side-297x284.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-blue-side-120x115.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-blue-side-768x734.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The MIPS Safety System claims to lower the chance of brain injury. The Comete SL uses extended rear coverage that enhances back-of-the-head protection. You’ll also find side and rear reflective zones to improve visibility in low-light conditions.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-front-black-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1005\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-front-black-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Mavic Comete SL Mips Helmet front black\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-front-black-jpeg.webp 1005w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-front-black-236x300.webp 236w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-front-black-94x120.webp 94w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-front-black-768x978.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-backside-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"1222\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-backside-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Mavic Comete SL Mips Helmet backside\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-backside-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-backside-297x284.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-backside-120x115.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Mavic-Comete-SL-Mips-Helmet-backside-768x733.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Mavic Comete SL MIPS Retails &amp; Details</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $190</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>XRD memory foam</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Classic strap buckle</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Glasses Garage with rubber retainers</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Reflective highlights</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Ponytail compatibility</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Mavic Care 3-year warranty and crash replacement program</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Weight: 280g</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.mavic.com/en-us\" target=\"_blank\">Mavic.com</a></em></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/mavic-comete-sl-mips-helmet/\">The New Mavic Comete SL Mips Helmet Promises Perfect Blend of Airflow and Speed</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"ebe2676f2c3b7bc2f48679a0698f1fd39aa9ee465229d24465138ed910705a0b","category":"Cycling"}